  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together smoky paprika, crispy sumac, garlic powder, kosher salt, and black pepper.",
    "Thread chicken pieces onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Brush skewers with olive oil and sprinkle spice mixture evenly over chicken.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until chicken is cooked through.",
    "Transfer skewers to a plate and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
